  "commentary": "With SPX at 6774.87 just below the GEX flip at 6771, dealers are in positive gamma territory and likely selling this bounce after the recent -2.3% move, providing resistance into the massive 6800 gamma wall (+6721.8M). The PIN regime with heavy positive gamma concentration between 6775-6800 should create strong mean-reverting forces, capping upside momentum as dealers hedge by selling calls/covering puts on any rally attempts. Watch for rejection at the 6780 (+4437.7M) and 6800 levels where dealer selling pressure intensifies, with support forming around the flip strike at 6771.\n\nBottom line: expect the market to get pinned between 6770-6800 with dealers capping rallies.",
